        "disabled": false,
        "info": "Requires rapid/MainModuleEGM.mod loaded on the controller (the top group loads it), a UDPUC transmission protocol named EGM_PC configured on the controller (RobotStudio > Controller > Configuration > Communication > Transmission Protocol, Remote Port = 6510, needs a controller restart), and a firewall rule on this Node-RED host allowing inbound UDP 6510. See the EGM section of CLAUDE.md / README.md."
